# Runner-image profiles. One Xcode version per line; `#`-prefixed
# lines are comments. The first non-comment line is the **default
# profile** — the chart's `runnersFleet.runnerImage` digest pin
# tracks it. The rest are additional profiles customers can pin to
# from their workflows.
#
# Each release rebuilds every profile against the matching
# `ghcr.io/tuist/macos-tahoe-xcode:<dashes>` base, so the matching
# tag must already be published by `macos-xcode-image.yml`.
